# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation CLIP+ Launcher
# Author: Jonathan Cheong, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-13
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Obfuscated use of Clip.exe to execute PowerShell
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_hktl_invoke_obfuscation_clip.yml

CommandLine IN ("*/c*", "*/r*") CommandLine="*cmd*" CommandLine="*&&*" CommandLine="*clipboard]::*" CommandLine="*-f*"